---

This exploration of the Telesterion at Eleusis combines:
- Rigorous first-principles acoustic physics
- Speculative Z² curiosities (for fun, not science)

The physics calculations are based on established equations.
The Z² connections are acknowledged as coincidences, not claims.

Use freely. Cite if helpful.
